title: Kylie Jenner dons midnight blue wig at Hollywood studio
text:
Kylie Jenner wigged out at a studio in Hollywood Wednesday where she reunited with her 27-year-old boyfriend Tyga (born Michael Nguyen-Stevenson).
The 19-year-old reality starlet covered her natural raven bob with a recycled 'midnight blue' hairpiece she debuted nearly a year ago.
The make-up mogul was dressed way down in a b&w tracksuit and matching sneakers, which were likely courtesy of her latest brand ambassadorship with Puma.
Scroll down for video

The Grammy-nominated rapper - sporting a tangerine sweatsuit - has a four-year-old son King with Kylie's future sister-in-law Blac Chyna.
Once safely inside, Kylie - who boasts 123.9M followers - began perpetually filming Snapchat selfies and teased: 'Working on a lil somethin!'
The vainglorious socialite also aimed her cell phone camera at the chain-strapped Gucci purse she brought along.
